text: <@U0260V4K1>: <@U02F9CXTL> Did you guys have an idea of what would be on the unassigned cubby screens? Will this change per cubby template of be a Workshop default? Do all the Cubbies have to be on at the same time?
It's on our list of things to be designed, but no we haven't gotten to it yet. I think, for now, we should plan on unassigned cubbies using a single design regardless of template.
